{
  "application": "LSF",
  "details": {
    "queue": "lowpriority",
    "gpu_resources": {
      "num": 1,
      "mode": "exclusive_process"
    },
    "container_image": "docker.optum.com/dhanley2/bert:cgan_build",
    "nodes": 1,
    "processors": "span[ptile=4]",
    "output_file": "log_train_%J",
    "command": "cd /share/dhanley2/recursion/scripts/$WDIR  && python3 train.py  \
            --logmsg recursion-pytorch-onecycle --nbags 20  --epochs 60 --fold $FOLD  --lr 0.0001 --batchsize 16 --workpath scripts/$WDIR  \
            --cutmix_prob 1.0 --beta 1.0  --imgpath data/mount/512X512X6/ --weightsname weights/pytorch_model_densenet$FOLD.bin",
    "python_script": "train.py",
    "script_arguments": [
      "--logmsg",
      "recursion-pytorch-onecycle",
      "--nbags",
      "20",
      "--epochs",
      "60",
      "--fold",
      "$FOLD",
      "--lr",
      "0.0001",
      "--batchsize",
      "16",
      "--workpath",
      "scripts/$WDIR",
      "--cutmix_prob",
      "1.0",
      "--beta",
      "1.0",
      "--imgpath",
      "data/mount/512X512X6/",
      "--weightsname",
      "weights/pytorch_model_densenet$FOLD.bin"
    ]
  }
}
